nodes.title: Positive prompt: Part 3
widgets_values: The same woman continues walking down the boulevard, lace dress shimmering softly in the golden light. She walks past a well-dressed 1920s gentleman in a tailored suit and hat standing on the sidewalk. The man briefly turns his head to look back at her, quietly captivated by her elegance, while she keeps walking forward with composed confidence, gaze ahead, expression calm and self-assured. The camera tracks her movement from the front, the gentleman falling slightly out of focus in the background, Parisian architecture and café awnings framing the scene, subtle film-grain texture, restrained romantic atmosphere.

nodes.title: Positive prompt: Part 4
widgets_values: The woman reaches the corner of the street and continous walking past an ornate iron streetlamp, the city opening wider behind her with rooftops and balconies stretching into the distance. She shifts the fur-trimmed coat more securely over her arm as a gentle breeze moves through the boulevard, lifting a few strands of her chestnut finger-wave bob and softly fluttering the lace overlay of her dress. She looks at the viewer with a faint, confident half-smile, poised and serene. The light warms toward early evening, creating a soft golden halo along the lace and satin, cinematic analog-film mood, timeless and elegant closing frame.

nodes.title: Positive prompt: Part 2
widgets_values: The same 27-year-old French woman, same deep-champagne satin lace dress and chestnut finger-wave bob, now holding the dark fur-trimmed coat folded gracefully over one arm. She rises slowly from the marble café table and steps away from her chair with elegant posture, the lace overlay catching the warm late-afternoon light as she begins to walk along the Parisian street terrace. The camera follows her from a gentle three-quarter angle, lingering on the delicate movement of the lace fabric and the subtle sway of her dress as she walks, Haussmann façades and wrought-iron balconies softly blurred behind her, vintage analog-film look, warm cinematic glow, calm and confident motion.

nodes.title: Positive prompt: Part 1
widgets_values:
A 27-year-old French woman seated at a small round marble café table on a Parisian street terrace in the late afternoon, elegant and poised, warm golden sunlight brushing across her face. She has delicate oval features, warm brown eyes, faint freckles across the bridge of her nose, and a refined 1920s chestnut bob with sculpted finger waves framing her cheeks. She wears a deep-champagne satin evening dress with an intricate floral lace overlay across the bodice and sleeves, scalloped lace neckline shimmering softly in the light. A rich dark fur-trimmed coat rests loosely draped over her shoulders, the fabric hanging in a relaxed, fashionable way.

The motion begins gently as she lifts her hands to slowly slip the coat off her shoulders in a graceful, downward motion, revealing more of the detailed lace dress. She holds the coat over one arm. The camera stays close and intimate as the coat slides down with soft movement, vintage cinematic lighting, shallow depth of field, quiet Parisian street architecture blurred in the background, analog-film atmosphere, elegant and timeless.
